160
00:13:54.801 --> 00:13:57.204
Along with all of his
investments. his bank accounts...

161
00:13:57.337 --> 00:13:58.647
everything.

162
00:13:58.671 --> 00:14:02.042
You are executor and
beneficiary until your death.

163
00:14:02.175 --> 00:14:05.588
