255
00:19:19.392 --> 00:19:21.027
Hey. girls?

256
00:19:26.132 --> 00:19:27.234
Want to be friends?

257
00:19:28.268 --> 00:19:29.178
Me?

258
00:19:29.202 --> 00:19:30.203
