262
00:19:34.607 --> 00:19:35.618
You sure?

263
00:19:35.642 --> 00:19:37.176
Pretty sure. Yeah.

264
00:19:41.414 --> 00:19:43.192
Hi.

265
00:19:43.216 --> 00:19:44.760
